# RadioChipGroup

A set of options presented as chips with only one option to select.

If you need to allow selecting more than one option, consider using [<mark>`CheckboxChipGroup`</mark>]({base}/docs/components/checkbox-chip-group). If you need more customization for the chips, such as their slots, take a look at [<mark>`RadioChip`</mark>]({base}/docs/components/radio-chip), the building block of this component.

